"{\"uid\": \"mercurynews.com-2024-07-30-what-to-watch-at-the-paris-olympics-on-wednesday-july-31\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Today's e-Edition  Get Morning Report and other email newsletters    Get Morning Report and other email newsletters  Today's e-Edition  Trending:  Katie Ledeckyis an overwhelming favorite to claim her first gold of these Games with one of her best events in the pool highlighting Wednesday's action at the2024 Paris Olympics.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 325, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 310, \"end\": 324, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Paris Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Here is a guide of what to look out for:  When the women's 1,500-meter freestyle made its debut on the Olympic program in Tokyo three years ago, Ledecky won by more than a four-second margin.\", \"from\": 327, \"to\": 518, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 449, \"end\": 454, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.974364258132568, \"rank\": 0.026277972926041226, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This time it could be an even bigger margin.\", \"from\": 520, \"to\": 564, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Ledecky won her heat Tuesday by more than a half-lap ahead of Simona Quadarella of Italy.\", \"from\": 566, \"to\": 655, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 628, \"end\": 645, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simona_Quadarella\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Simona Quadarella\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simona_Quadarella\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simona_Quadarella\"}, {\"begin\": 649, \"end\": 654, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy\", \"score\": 0.9720220171696118, \"rank\": 0.019558186198256996, \"text\": \"Italy\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 1,500 final is scheduled for 9:13 p.m. CEST (3:13 p.m. EDT).\", \"from\": 657, \"to\": 721, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Ledecky's only medal so far in Paris was a bronze in the 400 free.\", \"from\": 723, \"to\": 789, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 754, \"end\": 759, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.999999999154852, \"rank\": 8.450811934731926e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The other swimming finals on Wednesday will be held between 8:30 p.m. CEST (2:30 p.m. EDT) and about 10:45 p.m. CEST (4:45 p.m. EDT).\", \"from\": 791, \"to\": 924, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"They include the women's 100 free, the men's 200 butterfly, the men's 200 breaststroke and the men's 100 free.\", \"from\": 925, \"to\": 1035, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Themen's triathlonscheduled for Tuesday was postponed because of concerns about the water quality in the Seine River.\", \"from\": 1037, \"to\": 1154, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It was rescheduled for Wednesday, when the women's competition is also slated to be held.\", \"from\": 1155, \"to\": 1244, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But both will happen only if water tests show acceptablelevels of E. coli and other bacteria.\", \"from\": 1246, \"to\": 1339, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Friday is also planned as a backup date.\", \"from\": 1340, \"to\": 1380, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"However, storms or rain are forecast Tuesday night through Thursday, which could complicate rescheduling because rain generally causes bacteria levels in the Seine to rise.\", \"from\": 1382, \"to\": 1554, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1540, \"end\": 1545, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 0.9999963411320184, \"rank\": 3.2286913538557874e-06, \"text\": \"Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If Wednesday's races do go ahead, the women will start at 8 a.m. CEST (2 a.m. EDT) and the men will start at 10:45 a.m. CEST (4:45 a.m. EDT).\", \"from\": 1556, \"to\": 1697, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1621, \"end\": 1625, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Central_European_Summer_Time\", \"score\": 0.977196744477993, \"rank\": 0.02333537811174766, \"text\": \"CEST\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Central_European_Summer_Time\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Central_European_Summer_Time\"}, {\"begin\": 1676, \"end\": 1680, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Central_European_Summer_Time\", \"score\": 0.977196744477993, \"rank\": 0.02333537811174766, \"text\": \"CEST\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Central_European_Summer_Time\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Central_European_Summer_Time\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Still chasing the only big title he lacks after getting past longtime rival Rafael Nadal,Novak Djokovicfaces Dominik Koepfer of Germany in the third round at Roland Garros.\", \"from\": 1699, \"to\": 1871, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1775, \"end\": 1787, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Rafael Nadal\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\"}, {\"begin\": 1808, \"end\": 1823, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dominik_Koepfer\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Dominik Koepfer\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dominik_Koepfer\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dominik_Koepfer\"}, {\"begin\": 1827, \"end\": 1834, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany\", \"score\": 0.9877322844489654, \"rank\": 0.005032502240203377, \"text\": \"Germany\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Carlos Alcaraz, who won the French Open at the same venue last month, plays Roman Safiullin of Russia.\", \"from\": 1873, \"to\": 1975, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1873, \"end\": 1887, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Alcaraz\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Carlos Alcaraz\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Alcaraz\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Alcaraz\"}, {\"begin\": 1949, \"end\": 1964, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Roman_Safiullin\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Roman Safiullin\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Roman_Safiullin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Roman_Safiullin\"}, {\"begin\": 1968, \"end\": 1974, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\", \"score\": 0.7503198137832688, \"rank\": 0.23201706097726463, \"text\": \"Russia\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The men's all-around final in gymnastics is scheduled for 5:30 p.m. CEST (11:30 EDT).\", \"from\": 1977, \"to\": 2062, \"